The paper discusses a formalization of a common pattern in meta-learning approaches in deep learning and reinforcement learning, and presents a general-purpose algorithm and a library for implementing similar approaches. This work is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
